#

Chickpea Salad with Cucumbers and Feta

10 min
$6
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthyNo-Cook

Description

A refreshing and nutritious salad bursting with flavors of fresh cucumbers, creamy feta, and protein-packed chickpeas.

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • red onion: 1/4 small
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup
